social_outreach.body:
Subject: Story Pitch — {{your_name}}, {{niche}} Creator Building {{brand_name}}

Hi {{editor_name}},

I'm {{your_name}}, a {{niche}} content creator based in {{location}} with {{follower_count}} followers across Instagram and TikTok.

I thought your audience would connect with my story: {{one_sentence_story_hook}}.

Some context:
• I've grown my audience from {{starting_followers}} to {{current_followers}} in {{timeframe}}
• I recently {{notable_achievement}} (e.g. landed a brand deal, launched a product, hit X views)
• My audience is {{audience_description}} — {{age_range}}, passionate about {{niche}}

I'd love to be featured in {{publication_name}} or contribute a guest piece on {{story_angle}}. Happy to provide photos, stats, or a quote — whatever is most useful.

Attached is my media kit. Looking forward to connecting.

Best,
{{your_name}}
{{your_email}} | {{your_website}}

{{hook_line}} 👇

{{2-3 sentence description of what they'll find — your product, portfolio, booking link, etc.}}

Everything you need is in my bio 🔗

{{relevant_hashtags}}

💬 {{engagement_question — e.g. 'Drop a ❤️ if you want more of this' or 'Comment LINK and I'll DM you directly'}}

{{attention_grabbing_opener}} 🙋

I want to hear from YOU:
{{question_1}}
{{question_2 (optional)}}

{{why_this_matters_to_you_and_them — 1-2 sentences showing you care about their input}}

Drop your answer in the comments ⬇️ I read every single one.

{{hashtags}}

Hey {{creator_name}}! 👋 Huge fan of your {{specific_video_or_series}} — the way you {{what_you_love_about_their_content}} is genuinely great.

I'm {{your_name}}, I make {{your_content_type}} content ({{your_follower_count}} followers). I think a collab between us could go crazy — our audiences overlap a lot.

Would you be down for a:
→ Duet / Stitch on {{video_idea}}
→ Or a joint TikTok on {{topic}}

Either way, open to whatever feels natural for you. Just wanted to shoot my shot 😄

— {{your_name}} @{{your_handle}}

Subject: {{your_name}} — Rates & Partnership Info

Hi {{their_name}},

Thanks for reaching out — I'd love to work together!

I've attached my rate card with full pricing, but here's a quick summary:

📸 Single Instagram Post: {{ig_post_rate}}
🎬 Instagram Reel: {{reel_rate}}
📱 TikTok Video: {{tiktok_rate}}
📦 Content Package (3 posts): {{package_rate}}

All rates include usage rights for {{usage_period}} and {{number_of_revisions}} revision round.

I'm flexible on format and always open to discussing what works for your campaign goals. A few brands I've worked with: {{past_brands_or_'this would be our first partnership'}}.

Happy to jump on a quick call to align on the brief. What does your timeline look like?

Best,
{{your_name}}
{{your_email}} | {{your_instagram_or_website}}

Subject: Affiliate / Ambassador Application — {{your_name}}, {{niche}} Creator

Hi {{brand_name}} team,

I'm {{your_name}}, a {{niche}} content creator with {{follower_count}} followers on {{primary_platform}}. I've been genuinely using and loving {{specific_product_or_product_line}} for {{how_long}} — it's become a staple in my {{how_you_use_it — e.g. 'daily routine / setup / workflow'}}.

I'd love to apply to your affiliate or ambassador program. Here's a quick snapshot:
• Platform: {{platform}} | Followers: {{follower_count}} | Avg engagement: {{engagement_rate}}%
• Audience: {{age_range}}, {{location}}, passionate about {{niche}}
• Past brand partnerships: {{past_brands_or_'this would be our first partnership'}}

I'd create authentic content that showcases {{product}} in a real, relatable way — no forced ads. I believe in the product and I think my audience would too.

Let me know if you'd like my full media kit or more details. Would love to chat!

— {{your_name}}
{{your_email}} | {{your_instagram}}
